issue.title: Flood fill algorithm has false positives / false negatives
issue.body: Sometimes flood fill is considered successful even though it's impossible for the algorithm to get there from the player's position. And sometimes the other way around happens.

issue.title: Player occasionally is stuck inside wall upon spawning
issue.body: Sometimes the player is stuck in a solid wall, requiring a game over.
